            . I am a farmer, and was at Brentford, and saw Hitchcock buying the horse of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260622-36-person308">
                  WILLIAM 
                  DURBAN
               <interp inst="t18260622-36-person308" type="surname" value="DURBAN"></interp>
